SyncState *


IMAPStore mxroute_remote
Host glacier.mxrouting.net
Port 993
TLSType IMAPS
UserCmd "echo $MBSYNC_USER"
PassCmd "echo $MBSYNC_PASS"

MaildirStore mxroute_local
Path ~/mail/mxroute/
Inbox ~/mail/mxroute/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel mxroute
Far :mxroute_remote:
Near :mxroute_local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes


